    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Cold Email Writer\\n\",\"**NLP Project 53 of 100** — Generate personalized outbound emails using templates and LLMs.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, re, requests\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"prospects = [\\n    {'name':'Sarah Chen','company':'TechCorp','role':'VP Engineering','industry':'SaaS'},\\n    {'name':'Mark Johnson','company':'DataFlow','role':'CTO','industry':'Analytics'},\\n    {'name':'Lisa Park','company':'CloudFirst','role':'Head of ML','industry':'Cloud'},\\n]\\n\\ndef template_email(prospect):\\n    return f\\\"\\\"\\\"Subject: Quick question about {prospect['company']}'s {prospect['industry']} stack\\n\\nHi {prospect['name'].split()[0]},\\n\\nI noticed {prospect['company']} is doing impressive work in {prospect['industry']}. As {prospect['role']}, you're likely thinking about scaling your infrastructure.\\n\\nWe help {prospect['industry']} companies reduce deployment time by 40%. Would a quick 15-minute call make sense?\\n\\nBest,\\n[Your Name]\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\nfor p in prospects:\\n    print(template_email(p))\\n    print('---')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"def llm_email(prospect, model='qwen3:1.7b'):\\n    prompt = f\\\"\\\"\\\"Write a personalized cold email to {prospect['name']}, {prospect['role']} at {prospect['company']} ({prospect['industry']}). Keep it under 100 words, professional, with a clear CTA. /no_think\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    try:\\n        r = requests.post('http://localhost:11434/api/generate',json={'model':model,'prompt':prompt,'stream':False},timeout=60)\\n        return r.json().get('response','')\\n    except: return 'Ollama unavailable.'\\n\\nprint(llm_email(prospects[0]))\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Templates ensure consistency** and compliance.\\n\",\"- **LLMs add personalization** and creative variation.\\n\",\"- **For production, A/B test subject lines** and opening hooks.\\n\",\"- **Always include opt-out links** for email compliance.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
